title: Oberni Teats Size 1, Slow Flow Suitable for 0~3 Months Newborn Baby, Breast-Like Soft Silicone Nipples Fits Oberni Wide-Neck Baby Bottles, Pack of 2
features: Material: Made of premium-quality food-grade silicone, they're BPA and BPS-free, non-toxic, odor-free, skin-like soft, flexible, and durable. Safe for your baby's latch.

Size: Oberni free slow teats include 4 sizes, size 1 with free slow, suitable for 0~3 months, size 2 with medium free suitable for 3~6 months, size 3 with large flow suitable for 6~12 larger babies, size 4 with fast flow ideal for 12+ months big babies or toddlers.
Anti-Colic: With an air-free vented design, ideal for reducing colic and gas, spitting up, and increasing comfort.
Breast-Like: Adopted the mom breast-like shape design, which provides better latching for newborn babies, without confusion between breast and bottle feeding.
Fit: Oberni Size 1/2/3/4 ("S" M" "L" +"), 2/4 Packs teats fits all Oberni baby bottles (Not including the off-centered series, and water bottle)
